Company Overview of Tokio Marine Asset Management Co., Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Tokio Marine Asset Management Co., Ltd. is a privately owned investment manager. It provides its services to corporate pension funds, other institutional investors, corporate clients, individual customers, and public investment trusts. The firm manages separate client focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It also manages private equities and other alternative vehicles for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of Asia including Japan. It invests in stocks of companies including small cap companies using Growth at a Reasonable Price (GARP) as the investment style. The firm also invests in fixed income securities including bonds. It benchmarks the per...
Tokio Marine Asset Management Co., Ltd. is a privately owned investment manager. It provides its services to corporate pension funds, other institutional investors, corporate clients, individual customers, and public investment trusts. The firm manages separate client focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It also manages private equities and other alternative vehicles for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of Asia including Japan. It invests in stocks of companies including small cap companies using Growth at a Reasonable Price (GARP) as the investment style. The firm also invests in fixed income securities including bonds. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the TOPIX Index, Russell-Nomura Small Index, MSCI AC Far East Free ex-Japan Index, MSCI AC Asia Pacific ex-Japan Index, and NOMURA Bond Performance Index. The firm employs a combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis with bottom-up and top-down stock picking approaches while making its investments. It conducts in-house research while building its portfolio. The firm operates as a subsidiary of Tokio Marine and Nichido Fire Insurance Co., Ltd. and was founded in December 1985. Tokio Marine Asset Management Co., Ltd. is based in Tokyo, Japan.
